data.description: Welcome to your new 3 bedroom 2 bathroom custom home on an acre with horse privileges including 3 stalls, tack room and additional space to build a round pen, arena, or more stalls. Enjoy being tucked away at the end of a private road with picturesque mountain views and privacy galore. Enjoy the warmth of sunny days by your very own above-ground pool in your private backyard, perfect for relaxation and entertaining.  This home presents an incredible opportunity to embrace the beauty of rural living while enjoying the comfort of a custom-designed home, private backyard oasis. and all close to shopping and restaurants. Did I mention there is no HOA!  Don't miss your chance to experience this unique opportunity!
